data.description: Spacious well-appointed home with a variety of desirable features. Highlights include over 3100 sq ft of above-ground living space offering plenty of room for comfortable living. The lower level is finished. The recently updated kitchen has stainless steel appliances, large center island, and granite hard surfaces. The large family room, formal living, and dining rooms provide different areas for various activities and gatherings. The home boasts a 1st floor office, mudroom w/built-ins, 4 beds up, large loft area, 2 full baths, plus the convenience of 2nd flr laundry. Large primary ensuite is likely to provide a comfortable retreat within the home. Large patio w/oversize lot (.64 acres), w/ an inclusion of a newer Kayak pool (2023) adds a superior recreational element to this property!
